data.description: Move-in Ready!  All you need to do is unpack your suitcase...  Open Concept: living room, kitchen and dining all in one space.  The kitchen has white cabinets, stainless steel appliances and a CENTER island!    Off of the dining area is a sliding glass door that opens up to a patio and an expansive yard; perfect for barbecuing,  entertaining or playing.   The second floor has a primary ensuite with a large walk-in closet and ceiling fan.  Bedrooms two (2) and three (3) are generous in size and share a full bath. All bedrooms have neutral carpeting.   Laundry room, yes, it is a room, and it is on the second floor. No more carrying baskets of laundry up and down the staris.  Your knees and back will thank you!   The two car garage has an EV charging outlet, electric garage door opener and a water purifing system (Aqua Feel Solutions) that does convey with the home.   HOA, Elite Managment - fees $40.00 per month paid on a quartley basis.  Washer/Dryer and Stainless Steel GE Refridgerator, and all window blinds convey with home.  $600 carpet cleaning consession at closing.
